ZE_POTC_V3_4fix
MAP UPDATED FOR NEW CSS
CHANGES:
fixed the bugs from the update
new waterfall
no more spawnkill but teleports
some small changes
have fun

Make your way from 2 different spawns through the native village, caves and rivers. Jump through waterfalls and defend the mill. Ride the big wheel from PotC. In the end the Black Pearl awaits you and will shoot its cannons for zombie rape :D

Special Features:

-Jack Sparrows Pistol. Rightclick for zombie backboost.

-A secret way if you master the wheel. Look at the map after the second bridge in the hut which way to take. otherwise...

-Random way selection every round. The cave way or the river part.

Greetings FreeZe

PS: leave some good comments :)
